message: Removed the content again (not entire paragraph, just evidenced that is not verifiable) based on the theory provided on the article talk page.  If this is an in accurate edit please explain!

Removing "HelloFresh has been criticized for the excessive packaging of their delivered meals, leading to waste" as this was said by one person, Chef Richard Corrigan, who is not an expert on sustainable packaging. Additionally, other reputable sources note all of HelloFresh's commitment to sustainable packaging (https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180320006435/en/HelloFresh-Acquires-Green-Chef).
